nominatedCompanyDetailsGuidance.title = Company Details
nominatedCompanyDetailsGuidance.heading = Provide your nominated company details
nominatedCompanyDetailsGuidance.caption = Nominated company details
nominatedCompanyDetailsGuidance.paragraph1 = You’ll need to enter the nominated company’s details so we can confirm your company and link it to the correct HMRC records.
nominatedCompanyDetailsGuidance.paragraph2 = You’ll be asked to provide your:
nominatedCompanyDetailsGuidance.bulletPoint1 = Company Registration Number (CRN)
nominatedCompanyDetailsGuidance.bulletPoint2 = Unique Taxpayer Reference (UTR)
nominatedCompanyDetailsGuidance.paragraph3 = These details must match Companies House records. If they do not, you will not be able to register for the service.
nominatedCompanyDetailsGuidance.inset.text = If your organisation is not registered with Companies House, nominate a company in your group with a CRN to register. If no company in your group has a CRN, contact HMRC using your usual compliance contact or existing support channels.